A great recognition 👨‍🍳
Du Lac et Du Parc Grand Resort is proud to share with you a great achievement of our Executive Chef.

Since last December, Marco Brink has joined the prestigious team of @castalimenti, an Italian excellence in training for catering professionals.

His entry into the famous school of "world champions" ( Cast Alimenti boasts 21 world cups in its palmares) founded by @iginio.massari  and @vittoriosantoro_castalimenti, represents the crowning achievement of an adventure that began 23 years ago at Du Lac et Du Parc Grand Resort.

Experience, dedication and innovation: these are the 3 key factors that, from 1999 to today, have contributed to the growth of Marco and, together with him, of Du Lac et Du Parc Grand Resort.

Thank you for making us part of this important recognition, bravo Marco! 🎉
